WEBVTT

00:00:28.196 --> 00:00:30.347
we can live healthier
and more beautifully.

00:00:30.371 --> 00:00:33.992
Check out this landscape
in Santa Fe, New Mexico.

00:00:34.771 --> 00:00:37.913
Just notice what kinds of words
and feelings come to mind.

00:00:39.588 --> 00:00:43.271
This landscape was watered
with treated sewage water.

00:00:43.892 --> 00:00:45.652
Does that change anything for you?

00:00:46.458 --> 00:00:48.716
I imagine it might.

00:00:50.191 --> 00:00:51.482
And that's OK.

00:00:52.897 --> 00:00:55.094
How we feel about this

00:00:55.118 --> 00:00:58.565
is going to determine exactly
how innovative we can be.

